Berkshire Hathaway Posts Oper EPS $1,593, Est. $1,149

-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 
2011-05-06T21:20:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/berkshire-operating-profit-of-1-593-a-share-exceeds-analysts-estimates.html
(Corrects estimate in headline and text.)  Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A)  said it had
first-quarter operating profit of $1,593 a share. The average
estimate from a Bloomberg survey of analysts was $1,148 a share.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  